silex-packages signing key
==========================

This directory holds the RSA public key used to sign APKINDEX.tar.gz.

The private key lives in GitHub Actions secrets (SILEX_PKG_RSA).
The public key (SILEX_PKG_RSA_PUB) is written here by CI and committed.

To generate a new key pair (run once, store private key in repo secrets):

    abuild-keygen -a -n -i

The -i flag installs the public key into /etc/apk/keys/ automatically.
Copy the private key to SILEX_PKG_RSA and the public key to SILEX_PKG_RSA_PUB
in the repository's Actions secrets.

The Silex base image ships with silex-packages.rsa.pub pre-installed in
/etc/apk/keys/ so that `apk update` trusts this repository.
